I have lived a lifetime of abuse where my ex acted just like Amber " oh you're fine, "I didn't do that you did" there are women and men who are in fact being abused daily. Men and women both who can not leave the relationship for a number of reasons. You have children with this person, will this person harm you and or your loved ones if you leave.  It sickens me that she would put this bright and brilliant man through this. No, he isn't perfect and yes he has a long battle to face after all of this to stay sober. Everyone has their Demons but Amber taking photos to humiliate him and laugh behind his back to her friends is disturbing and sick. 
I really hope Johnny wins! And even if he doesn't, it really took courage to fight and jot give up!
I love you Johnny and I am so proud of you!!! 
Own your darkness and your light!!!

column2:
Truth Matters and nobody should have to additionally fight to survive what is the further catastrophic destruction of their lives, purpose and core being of everything which constitutes a Life.  It is Secondary Abuse and far worse than what preceded it. That someone like this had to wait SIX YEARS to have his Voice heard, reveals a system which needs serious upheaval.  Lies, false allegations, and manipulation of Truth into its opposite narrative is secondary criminal abuse.  Not helped by allowing lawyers like hers to fight to ensure no answers can be given the chance of being truthfully responded to with full context.  Obstructing context should be prohibited where the fundamental purpose is supposed to represent Truth and Justice.   Half a Truth may be the wrong half.  Why does a Court in such cases ever allow and enable Truth to he restricted and left out of context?   
As for those whom are pathological liars and destroy lives with such unecessary cruel hatred, and no problems committing Perjury, there should be a special place in Hell for them (when eventually proven).  The years they have stolen from others, they should lose three-fold.   As for women whom make false allegations of sexual abuse, they should never roam free.  They are just as dangerous to genuine survivers, as the primary perpetrator(s).
She has destroyed so many lives, stolen so much that is irrecoverable, as well as unrecoverable, that nothing can remedy the damage she has inflicted upon so many.
And for what?  What was her reason to calculate such a hateful, cruel smear campaign?  Only pure hateful evil would destroy lives with lies.  
Ironically, despite highest importance above all else, nobody seems to have remembered the one year old infant who really matters too.
I hope JD rescues her too.  That she dies not end up in yet another System and gets a complete new life whilst still so young.   I hope JD does not forget to rescue her and that others start thinking about her too.  The most Innocent of all.  His Team are so amazing and she could not have a more protected life..
Finally, I hope each one of her legal team, whom have profited from this, donate every single Dollar they have received from this entire case to the Children's Charity whom have instead received nothing.  As well as a Trust Fund for her one year old daughter whilst paying JD's Legal Team for all work and costs in handling the legalities required for the one year old infant girl whom does not deserve to be forgotten in all this.  Only then, should a "Statue" follow.  Bob Geldof was/is the example of such a quietly discreet and altruistic act of selfless Love.  Nobody else should suffer.  Hatred can be replaced with fresh Love and Joy.  And something positive from such suffering which would Protect, Love and Heal.
Truth is that "rare bird" and rescuing everyone, to include a baby girl, will be to hear the song of that rare bird complete.
